{"tid":85289,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士行李變長城, 封車門阻人落車","createTime":"2017-01-18T08:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T09:50:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1dff36a58ac116372fb6215e62733e9d92f2ba4","tid":85289,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/rXich4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FrXich4.jpg&h=8912616e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=R5Po8f5GjK4hF73s51MjnoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=38f085df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 巴士變「貨車」已經並不鮮見，每次都引來網民炮轟，批評阻塞通道和影響行車安全。昨日再有網民分享照片，今次行李篋更變成「長城」堵塞車門，令乘客難以落車。 <br />\n<br />\n網民Fanny Mak在facebook「香港厚多士」群組中分享照片，拍攝了一輛來往屯門市中心和深圳灣口岸的B3X線巴士。相中可見巴士的下車門打開，但多個行李篋整齊地疊起，封住車門。發貼者稱當時有不少乘客起身等待落車，因此上下層都站滿人，但由於下車門被封，因此乘客只能從上車門落車。 <br />\n<br />\n不少網民都表示嘆息，稱巴士有上無落。也有人指落車要「跨欄」，或者乾脆把行李篋踢下車。亦有人揶揄要「包容」，又形容巴士變成「水貨專車」。另有網民批評司機允許乘客攜帶大量行李上車，但也有人對司機表示同情。 <br />\n<br />\n網民有話說 <br />\n<br />\nAlvin Siu：啲篋排得好整齊 <br />\n<br />\nConnie YU：有上無落 <br />\n<br />\nHoi Fung So：人哋辦年貨啫，包容下啦！ <br />\n<br />\nHO Pun Luk：水貨客專用巴士 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://on.fb.me/1L3m1ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.fb.me%2F1L3m1ro&d=R5Po8f5GjK4hF73s51MjnoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=91de493f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://on.fb.me/1L3m1ro</a>"},{"pid":"a5ac2577ef8208123c2a5d6516d6987d27bce4dd","tid":85289,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790de1f92f146192ed98daf69eaf862e1f20caa3","tid":85289,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:36:41.000Z","msg":"日日都係咁，濕濕碎"},{"pid":"1dadf738c9dffedd2429ec44498641cbe365f9e7","tid":85289,"uid":11082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:02:06.000Z","msg":"踢晒落車啦"},{"pid":"287dcb341cb654490a3ff8bf150a3a867d912ffb","tid":85289,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:15:25.000Z","msg":"多謝支那狗啦"},{"pid":"c3169c6c9b1330294d696cf910472a40d366d51b","tid":85289,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"B3x日日都咁樣<br />\n每次到屯市就有一大條車隊一齊入去"},{"pid":"879ddb4a932a7790a54926afe270f6f01d9b89fa","tid":85289,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}